58
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,200
Zrači.

59
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,480
Nikada nikoga niste ušli, niste vidjeli na terenu.

60
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:41,840
Na četiri metra kopane znači gore sve žive, gore naći ćete vodu.

61
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:57,680
